Privacy Policy

This privacy policy governs your use of the software application “Super Box” for mobile devices that was created by Jefferson Calheiros. The Application is a free application that does not collect any personal data or information.

The Application uses advertising provided by Google Admob. Admob may collect certain information such as your device type and unique device identifier, and may use cookies or other technologies to collect information about your use of the Application.

Please review the Google Admob privacy policy for further information on the data collection and use practices of Admob.

By using the Application, you are consenting to the data collection and use practices described in this privacy policy as well as the Google Admob privacy policy.

If you have any questions regarding privacy while using the Application, or have questions about our practices, please contact us via email at jeffersoncalheirosdev@gmail.com.

This policy may be updated from time to time for any reason. We will notify you of any changes to our Privacy Policy by posting the new Privacy Policy here. You are advised to consult this Privacy Policy regularly for any changes, as continued use is deemed approval of all changes.
